    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom-grade condition. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a factory-new unit, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure uncompromising reliability. This is a definitive opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-quality asset that represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
